{"tid":845371,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"窮人我求你哋千祈唔好生仔","createTime":"2018-10-02T14:57:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-02T14:57:41.000Z","uid":152186,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a439a85e4393f094e92e6af158de2c3d6a8c3dd7","tid":845371,"uid":152186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T14:57:41.000Z","msg":"害撚死佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n書都未讀完已經成日問個小朋友<br />\n大個咗養唔養佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同佢解釋外國唔主張要小朋友大個一定要養翻兩老<br />\n佢屌撚到上天<br />\n話我不孝<br />\n又話佢旨意哂我養佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但佢個仔乜閪都唔做<br />\n佢又唔出聲<br />\n大佬我自己讀書啲支出幾時有問過你攞<br />\n買野幾時要你俾錢<br />\n同你出街有邊次唔係請你食飯<br />\n同你有分歧<br />\n你就係咁屌我<br />\n所以窮人生仔真係正仆街<br />\n搞到個小朋友心理唔平衡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n鬧完繼續做個孝順小朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}